{"tid":731140,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"童年回憶-水滸歷險","createTime":"2018-07-06T03:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T13:13:30.000Z","uid":73693,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9a684bd63614b2a27112cbc730020701b1ac6525","tid":731140,"uid":73693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T03:25:23.000Z","msg":"遊戲名稱：歲月如歌水滸(改左易玩)<br />\n遊戲下載：<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1AvslvjwwxQH-BQbViazXOafg_U2uYuJt/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1AvslvjwwxQH-BQbViazXOafg_U2uYuJt%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=c9KDJrwBTBNzjMKrMG0jmsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=6655311e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1AvslvjwwxQH-BQbViazXOafg_U2uYuJt/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n公告群：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/F5R46UuU_9S91qqwbGiDCQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FF5R46UuU_9S91qqwbGiDCQ&d=c9KDJrwBTBNzjMKrMG0jmsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=0b5133e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/F5R46UuU_9S91qqwbGiDCQ</a><br />\n交流群 : <a href=\"https://t.me/神行太保戴宗Ser\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2F%E7%A5%9E%E8%A1%8C%E5%A4%AA%E4%BF%9D%E6%88%B4%E5%AE%97Ser&d=c9KDJrwBTBNzjMKrMG0jmsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=534fef57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/神行太保戴宗Ser</a><br />\n服務器經驗倍數：3倍經,151以下部份怪物10倍經, 怪物數量3-5倍 <br />\n多開限制: 最多3開<br />\n掘料成功率:100%<br />\n<br />\n升Lv <br />\n新手1-150LV升LV好快.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開3隻AC 1武僧 +1莊客 +1文人<br />\n然後都係跟返正圖咁升LV 掛英, 一開頭可能會慢少少.但之後就飛住咁升. 升到10LV記得去禮物大使拎新手裝+宋萬(加到好勁 夠打到150LV),升到大慨40LV 就去掛石門 石門D怪加左5倍經 會升得好快(. 記得不停執垃圾)<br />\n升到50LV就可以去禮物大使拎多套新手裝 同埋5張英雄卡(可以不停開分身刷 易隻英過去掛到50LV刷英雄卡當首抽咁刷 刷史進/林沖出黎) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後就開始飛升架啦. 呢個時候懶既可以繼續跟正圖掛機, 想升得快既 入大草打桃木怪,桃木精 <br />\n升到90入白芽掛埋佢上1轉, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  記得100LV要去禮物大使拎套101玄武裝(夠玩到170)<br />\n1轉之後應該有夠錢買套0轉1轉技書可以爆技加MP. 上到1轉就可以直接入千里掛爆. 千里D黑甲 銀甲 花都加晒5倍經 秒住掛機1日上150LV.之後睇下夠唔夠50條四草換個血牛披去頂怪, 或者去1轉魔王山刷裝 好易打 開隻英掛一陣都有幾件裝頂怪 (20萬入場費)  <br />\n大家有玩過都知, 150-170 / 215-230係比較難捱之外 其他都係飛住咁升,而且個SER怪既數量都多左2-3倍,同2-3倍經冇咩分別. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾日就可以2轉100.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裝侑:<br />\n魔王裝必須要有 升LV必備. (刷魔王山 1轉2轉 王15分鍾刷新) 呢D裝好多人都會有多 係群問下就會有人比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  自己打都係開隻英係到掛機刷1-2個鍾夠晒比3隻AC<br />\n聖火裝備:升LV+打王要有 (可以用水錢買火卷/去掛鐵礦石換火卷)<br />\n舊雀裝備: 用黎升極雀裝(可以買, 刷既話3000萬搞掂1套舊雀)<br />\n極雀裝備: 2轉要11萬防頂極雀 (改左開證任打12個鍾.唔洗限住時間打) (明王天魔200萬上限20秒完1場雀 所以點解叫大家開隻武僧玩)<br />\n極虎裝備: 目前物攻最勁既裝,全SER好少人有.(16萬防頂 好難打,而且要刷個陣都好煩所以冇咩人有.)<br />\n其他裝備GM都新增緊.<br />\n<br />\n字首珠:<br />\n7級珠,劉唐珠,高廉珠,金鼠珠等字首珠可以去雁門刷南瓜王出字首珠卡抽(直接入身)<br />\n其他勁珠例如史珠 林珠 魯珠 白珠 聖火珠 就要用歷練卡(上舊塔上到11層無論趺定上12層都會有最少1張)換 或者 抽月神寶盒<br />\n金牛珠就要抽潘盒<br />\n<br />\n坐騎:<br />\n抽潘盒 (金甲 金車 機甲 機車 朱雀 白虎 玄武之類有機率會係潘盒抽出)<br />\n或者刷宋家村換隻聖誕鹿騎 <br />\n或者刷料換隻紅牛騎用<br />\n呢兩隻騎都好勁 夠打晒所有裝<br />\n<br />\n寵物:<br />\n抽寵蛋會有機會出 雀虎玄武寵 機率都幾高下. <br />\n<br />\n英:<br />\n部份英雄都加強左 史進 林沖 宋萬 戴宗 2娘呢D.<br />\n勁英既話就同GM 用真錢買(入群問佢) 或者抽月神寶盒會出個張抽勁英既卡<br />\n3轉英要去邪化石門打王用碎片換/同GM買3轉英卡抽"},{"pid":"a42dabdd3adf8ed1c883b243ae3ee0accd53fb9b","tid":731140,"uid":73693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T14:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f423fac8cf3f294e15c4efc20ba0c39eb719be","tid":731140,"uid":58484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:13:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f10f77fe67f59e36a263166fa9bab7d62ef948ab","tid":731140,"uid":22322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a42dabdd3adf8ed1c883b243ae3ee0accd53fb9b","tid":731140,"uid":73693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T14:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T14:18:42.000Z","msg":"想問下隻GAME仲係唔係到?<br />\n想DOWN黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab6d8d6884a9164d2f54a86796a2eb6a38595b6","tid":731140,"uid":36026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f10f77fe67f59e36a263166fa9bab7d62ef948ab","tid":731140,"uid":22322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a42dabdd3adf8ed1c883b243ae3ee0accd53fb9b","tid":731140,"uid":73693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T14:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c